      "risk": "200ms SLA violated under high concurrency when many orders compete for the same couriers in a small area",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "SKIP LOCKED prevents blocking but may exhaust candidates. Pre-size the shortlist (top 10-20 instead of 5) to reduce second-round queries. Monitor p99 latency and add circuit breaker to return 503 rather than violate the latency SLA with a degraded response."
    },
    {
      "risk": "Operational complexity exceeds 2-engineer capacity (Patroni, PgBouncer, monitoring, on-call)",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Use a managed PostgreSQL service with synchronous replication support (AWS RDS Multi-AZ with synchronous commit, or Google Cloud SQL HA). This offloads failover management, backups, and monitoring to the cloud provider, dramatically reducing operational burden."
    }
  ],

